  "description": "A full choir heard from across a vast valley. Maximum stage, heavy low-pass filtering, high detune spread. The individual voices blur into collective texture. You cannot pick out words or notes — only the presence of many voices singing together at great distance. Portamento adds languid pitch movement.",
